Game.....: Ducati World Racing Challenge
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: March 2nd, 2001
Ripped.......: Nothing

Ducati World Racing Challenge features the entire range of Ducati bikes - past and present - and includes arcade yet realistic physics, and the utmost attention to the rich Ducati lifestyle. Race over 40 Ducati bikes - present and past, including Authentic Classic Ducatis. Ducati World Racing Challenge is the most absorbing and detailed motorcycle racing game ever with super smooth hi-rez graphics and is the best rider/bike interface ever seen in a bike racing title. 

Notes:
- Run UNPACK/INJECT prior to burning this game.
- This quality release was fixed to work on all territories. It's something that our competitors still seem to have trouble doing...